Problem Statement
-----------------
You are building a home automation system that controls various devices like lights, air conditioners, TVs, and security cameras. 
Each device has its own complex set of operations and interfaces. Design a simplified interface for users to activate common scenarios 
like "Leave Home", "Arrive Home", and "Movie Time" without needing to interact with each device individually.


Components
----------
1. Devices [AC, TV, Light, Cameras]
2. Remote (Facade)
3. Interface for remote